value.name: Ny standard for ventilation i bygninger - Dansk Standard
value.snippet: Om DS 447 - Ventilation i bygninger. Standarden DS 447 - Ventilation i bygninger - mekaniske, naturlige og hybride ventilationssystemer indeholder bestemmelser vedrørende projektering, udførelse, afprøvning og drift af ventilationssystemer, samt bestemmelser for produkter og komponenter, der anvendes til ventilationssystemerne.

value.name: Which country's code is +447? - Quora
value.snippet: No country's code is +447 +44 is the code for the United Kingdom. The 7 (07 within the UK) means that this is either a mobile phone (cellphone) or one of those “personal numbers” that you can buy and set to redirect to wherever you happen to be. I think pagers are in the 07 range as well, but I've not seen one of those for a couple of decades.

value.name: Where Is Country Code 447? - Reference.com
value.snippet: While 447 is not a country code, 44 is the country code for the United Kingdom and its dependencies. Seven is just the first number dialed after the country code. Most numbers beginning with seven in the United Kingdom are cell phone numbers. It is also assigned to personal numbers and pagers. To dial abroad, one must first dial a prefix number.
